{"tid":593781,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"762 業績討論區","createTime":"2018-03-15T09:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T06:23:41.000Z","uid":2843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47a4fbc88e15cca42613287ec2b63329c3326f73","tid":593781,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:27:21.000Z","msg":"無人討論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1161e9f91501ed334dea8675ef70a755d206df2e","tid":593781,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47a4fbc88e15cca42613287ec2b63329c3326f73","tid":593781,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:27:21.000Z","msg":"無人討論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"公布截至去年底止年度業績，純利18.3億元人民幣(下同)，同比增長192.5%，每股盈利7分，派末期息5.2分，上年同期並無派息。EBITDA達到814.3億元，同比增長2.4%。剔除光改項目相關的資產報廢淨損失後，淨利潤為40億元，同比增長540.5%，EBITDA為843.3億元，同比增6.1%。<br />\n<br />\n期內，營業收入2,748.3億元，同比增長0.2%。其中，服務收入穩步提升，達到2,490.2億元，同比增長4.6%。移動服務收入達到1,564.4億元，同比增長7.9%，高出行業平均2.2個百分點。固網業務實現服務收入908.7億元，同比下降0.9%，基本保持平穩。其中語音收入佔比下降至13.3%，固網業務結構進一步改善。<br />\n<br />\n2017年，公司在確保網絡競爭力的同時，資本開支同比大幅下降41.6%，為421.3億元。得益於收入逐步改善，及資本開支大幅下降，公司自由現金流達到429.2億元，同比提升16.3倍。同時受益於公司混合所有制改革引資順利完成，公司資本實力大幅增強，財務狀況更加穩健，資產負債率由上年同期的62.9%下降至46.8%。<br />\n<br />\n去年，移動出賬用戶全年淨增2,034萬戶，達到2.8416億戶，移動出賬用戶ARPU為48元，按年升3.5%，公司4G用戶淨增7,033萬戶，總數達到1.7488億戶，4G用戶市場份額同比提高3.7個百分點；4G用戶佔移動出賬用戶比例達到61.5%，同比提高21.9個百分點。移動手機數據流量達到77,860億MB，同比增長384%。<br />\n<br />\n2017年公司銷售通信產品成本發生266.4億元，同期銷售通信產品收入為258.1億元，銷售通信產品虧損為8.3億元，其中，終端補貼成本為12.5億元，同比下降59.1%。(ka/u)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2018-03-15 16:25。)"},{"pid":"381deb39736d7fe1d9ce0723894e95a21c111f01","tid":593781,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbed8d0dd05a693708b4316ada730f679757dae","tid":593781,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e56c53b51951c094f2eb3684fbf296484b6764","tid":593781,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢排日日插， 唉"},{"pid":"90a9a5eaf13906a55b6591807a48fa5b9a06f632","tid":593781,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c91ec24716e67a81308975501558279a5fca4be","tid":593781,"uid":21732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a9a5eaf13906a55b6591807a48fa5b9a06f632","tid":593781,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點不問價all in"},{"pid":"7dc2b85e6778f806fcd70895915892bae28d8bdc","tid":593781,"uid":75932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c91ec24716e67a81308975501558279a5fca4be","tid":593781,"uid":21732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a9a5eaf13906a55b6591807a48fa5b9a06f632","tid":593781,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點不問價all in"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:43:47.000Z","msg":"會不會再跌？ 想買四手"},{"pid":"8de7b1802176ddb1facfc3c668ad2e93da56448f","tid":593781,"uid":21732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dc2b85e6778f806fcd70895915892bae28d8bdc","tid":593781,"uid":75932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c91ec24716e67a81308975501558279a5fca4be","tid":593781,"uid":21732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a9a5eaf13906a55b6591807a48fa5b9a06f632","tid":593781,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime"